      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner. It runs great and has been well-maintained, perfect for someone who wants a solid car without the 'new car' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
